title: Redrum - Season 3
description:
Redrum - Season 3

When it comes to murder, no detective starts their search at the beginning of the crime. Rather, a murder investigation always begins with the body, after the deed is done. It is up to the police to piece together the story, moving backwards in time until they arrive at the root of the crime.

Ep 1 - The In Crowd
Ep 2 - At The End Of His Rope
Ep 3 - Family Values
Ep 4 - O Come All Ye Unfaithful
Ep 5 - The Miseducation Of Avis Banks
Ep 6 - A New Man
Ep 7 - Something Borrowed, Someone Blue
Ep 8 - The Girl In The Shower
Ep 9 - The Caned Crusader
Ep 10 - Murder, Who Wrote
Ep 11 - Families & Foes
Ep 12 - School House Rocked
